---

<Layout title="Sobre | Lucas Ramos">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-8">

    <!-- Voltar -->
    <a href="/" class="text-neonCyan font-mono text-xs hover:underline mb-10 inline-flex items-center gap-1 pt-only">&larr; VOLTAR</a>
    <a href="/" class="text-neonCyan font-mono text-xs hover:underline mb-10 inline-flex items-center gap-1 en-only">&larr; BACK</a>
    <a href="/" class="text-neonCyan font-mono text-xs hover:underline mb-10 inline-flex items-center gap-1 fr-only">&larr; RETOUR</a>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <header class="mb-16 pb-10 border-b border-surfaceHighlight">

      <!-- Nome + saudação -->
      <div class="mb-10">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-neonCyan mb-4 tracking-widest">lucasramos.dev ~/ $</p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight">
          Lucas<br/>
          <span class="text-neonLime">Ramos</span><span class="text-neonCyan">.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-textMuted mt-3 pt-only">São José, SC · trabalha remoto · dorme tarde</p>
        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-textMuted mt-3 en-only">São José, SC · works remote · sleeps late</p>
        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-textMuted mt-3 fr-only">São José, SC · télétravail · se couche tard</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio — texto legível em textMain -->
      <div class="max-w-2xl space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed mb-10">
        <div class="pt-only space-y-4 text-textMain">
          <p>Ando por aí com uma Canon tentando fotografar coisas antes que a luz vá embora.</p>
          <p>Gosto de pensar que gosto de trilha (apesar de odiar cada segundo delas), de fotografia que parece analógica, de cozinhar um negócio demorado num domingo e de explorar estradas sem muito plano.</p>
          <p>Este site é meio que um diário, uma galeria de fotos e um registro dos projetos que eu acho que valem a pena.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="en-only space-y-4 text-textMain">
          <p>I walk around with a Canon trying to photograph things before the light goes away.</p>
          <p>I like to think I enjoy hiking (despite hating every second of it), photography that looks like it could be film, cooking something that takes forever on a Sunday, and driving down roads without much of a plan.</p>
          <p>This site is kind of a diary, a photo gallery, and a record of the projects I think are worth keeping.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fr-only space-y-4 text-textMain">
          <p>Je me balade avec un Canon en essayant de photographier des trucs avant que la lumière parte.</p>
          <p>J'aime me convaincre que j'aime la randonnée (même si j'en déteste chaque seconde), la photographie qui ressemble à de l'argentique, cuisiner un truc qui prend des heures un dimanche, et explorer des routes sans trop de plan.</p>
          <p>Ce site c'est un peu un journal, une galerie de photos et un recueil des projets qui me semblent valoir la peine.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Currently -->
      <div class="mb-10 bg-surface border border-surfaceHighlight rounded-2xl p-5 max-w-lg">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-neonCyan mb-4 tracking-widest pt-only">// AGORA MESMO</p>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-neonCyan mb-4 tracking-widest en-only">// CURRENTLY</p>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-neonCyan mb-4 tracking-widest fr-only">// EN CE MOMENT</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 font-mono text-sm">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-neonLime flex-shrink-0">▸</span><span class="text-textMain pt-only">trabalhando em pipelines CDC na RD Station</span><span class="text-textMain en-only">building CDC pipelines at RD Station</span><span class="text-textMain fr-only">pipelines CDC chez RD Station</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-neonLime flex-shrink-0">▸</span><span class="text-textMain pt-only">voltando a estudar → Sistemas de Informação na UFSC</span><span class="text-textMain en-only">back to studying → Info Systems at UFSC</span><span class="text-textMain fr-only">retour aux études → Info à l'UFSC</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-neonLime flex-shrink-0">▸</span><span class="text-textMain pt-only">saindo pra fotografar sempre que dá</span><span class="text-textMain en-only">going out to shoot whenever I can</span><span class="text-textMain fr-only">sorties photo dès que possible</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-neonLime flex-shrink-0">▸</span><span class="text-textMain pt-only">construindo este site</span><span class="text-textMain en-only">building this site</span><span class="text-textMain fr-only">construisant ce site</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Gosto de / I like -->
      <div class="mb-10">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted mb-4 pt-only">coisas que gosto:</p>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted mb-4 en-only">things i like:</p>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted mb-4 fr-only">des trucs que j'aime :</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {['fotografia', 'cozinhar', 'Python (com moderação)', 'café', 'gatos', 'viajar de carro', 'música', 'ficar em casa'].map(tag => (
            <span class="font-mono text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-surface border border-surfaceHighlight text-textMain hover:border-neonLime/40 transition-colors">{tag}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/photography" class="font-mono text-xs px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-neonLime/10 border border-neonLime/30 text-neonLime hover:bg-neonLime/20 transition-colors pt-only">📷 ver álbuns</a>
        <a href="/photography" class="font-mono text-xs px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-neonLime/10 border border-neonLime/30 text-neonLime hover:bg-neonLime/20 transition-colors en-only">📷 see essays</a>
        <a href="/photography" class="font-mono text-xs px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-neonLime/10 border border-neonLime/30 text-neonLime hover:bg-neonLime/20 transition-colors fr-only">📷 voir essais</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/ramoslucas-lr" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="font-mono text-xs px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-surfaceHighlight border border-surfaceHighlight text-textMuted hover:text-neonCyan hover:border-neonCyan/30 transition-colors">GitHub ↗</a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ramoslucas-lr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="font-mono text-xs px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-surfaceHighlight border border-surfaceHighlight text-textMuted hover:text-neonCyan hover:border-neonCyan/30 transition-colors">LinkedIn ↗</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Experiência -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-neonCyan mb-2 pt-only">// O LADO PROFISSIONAL</h2>
      <h2 class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-neonCyan mb-2 en-only">// THE PROFESSIONAL SIDE</h2>
      <h2 class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-neonCyan mb-2 fr-only">// LE CÔTÉ PROFESSIONNEL</h2>
      <p class="text-textMuted text-xs font-mono mb-8 pt-only">(caso você esteja aqui por isso)</p>
      <p class="text-textMuted text-xs font-mono mb-8 en-only">(in case you're here for this)</p>
      <p class="text-textMuted text-xs font-mono mb-8 fr-only">(au cas où c'est pour ça que vous êtes là)</p>

      <div class="relative">
        <!-- linha vertical -->
        <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-surfaceHighlight ml-[7px] hidden sm:block"></div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
          {experiences.map((exp) => (
            <div class="sm:pl-8 relative group">
              <!-- dot -->
              <div class={`hidden sm:block absolute left-0 top-1 w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-2 ${exp.color === 'cyan' ? 'border-neonCyan bg-base group-hover:bg-neonCyan' : 'border-neonLime bg-base group-hover:bg-neonLime'} transition-colors`}></div>

              <div class="bg-surface border border-surfaceHighlight rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-opacity-60 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg">
                <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-3 mb-4">
                  <div>
                    <span class={`font-mono text-xs tracking-wider ${exp.color === 'cyan' ? 'text-neonCyan' : 'text-neonLime'}`}>{exp.company}</span>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mt-0.5 pt-only">{exp.role.pt}</h3>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mt-0.5 en-only">{exp.role.en}</h3>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mt-0.5 fr-only">{exp.role.fr}</h3>
                  </div>
                  <div class="text-right">
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted pt-only">{exp.period.pt}</p>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted en-only">{exp.period.en}</p>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted fr-only">{exp.period.fr}</p>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted mt-0.5 pt-only">{exp.location.pt}</p>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted mt-0.5 en-only">{exp.location.en}</p>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted mt-0.5 fr-only">{exp.location.fr}</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <ul class="space-y-1.5 mb-4">
                  {exp.bullets.pt.map((b) => (
                    <li class="text-sm text-textMuted pt-only flex gap-2"><span class="text-neonLime mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">›</span><span>{b}</span></li>
                  ))}
                  {exp.bullets.en.map((b) => (
                    <li class="text-sm text-textMuted en-only flex gap-2"><span class="text-neonLime mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">›</span><span>{b}</span></li>
                  ))}
                  {exp.bullets.fr.map((b) => (
                    <li class="text-sm text-textMuted fr-only flex gap-2"><span class="text-neonLime mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">›</span><span>{b}</span></li>
                  ))}
                </ul>

                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
                  {exp.tags.map((tag) => (
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-mono px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-surfaceHighlight text-textMuted">{tag}</span>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Skills -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-neonCyan mb-8 pt-only">// COMPETÊNCIAS TÉCNICAS</h2>
      <h2 class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-neonCyan mb-8 en-only">// TECHNICAL SKILLS</h2>
      <h2 class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-neonCyan mb-8 fr-only">// COMPÉTENCES TECHNIQUES</h2>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {skills.map((skill) => (
          <span class="font-mono text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-neonCyan/10 to-neonLime/10 hover:from-neonCyan/20 hover:to-neonLime/20 text-textMain transition-colors duration-200" style="border-image: linear-gradient(to right, var(--color-accent-1), var(--color-accent-2)) 1">
            {skill}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Formação & Certificações -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">

      <!-- Formação -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-neonCyan mb-6 pt-only">// FORMAÇÃO</h2>
        <h2 class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-neonCyan mb-6 en-only">// EDUCATION</h2>
        <h2 class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-neonCyan mb-6 fr-only">// FORMATION</h2>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <div class="bg-surface border border-surfaceHighlight rounded-2xl p-5">
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-neonLime">UFSC</span>
            <p class="font-bold text-sm mt-1 pt-only">Bacharelado em Sistemas de Informação</p>
